<p>主料</p> 
<p>玉米面(100g)，面粉(30g)，清水(适量)</p> 
<p>辅料</p> 
<p>玉米粒(50g)，青豆粒(50g)，胡萝卜粒(50g)，香葱(25g)，培根(50g)</p> 
<p>厨具</p> 
<p>平底锅</p> 
<p>步骤</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//149d/149de509c2d10bbc5e4094b6afca0c78.com/large/1921000281f7d2845a8c"></p> 
<p>1、香葱切粒；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//05f9/05f98964ac6436858d0a4775be7aa103.com/large/191f00029bbf8bd96ae9"></p> 
<p>2、胡萝卜切粒；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//a03b/a03b0f06afd3bbfadd24d1df72aa8293.com/large/191e0002ae7902bc4856"></p> 
<p>3、培根切粒；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4d15/4d15d98fbdef2173a9db280e09866c22.com/large/191400048fde4fd2ba0f"></p> 
<p>4、将香葱粒、胡萝卜粒、培根粒、玉米粒和青豆粒一起放进大碗；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b303/b3039dc089e45c400562e2f9bd30a3d7.com/large/19200002ad17e2c03b72"></p> 
<p>5、加入适量盐、糖和胡椒粉（糖可以稍多一点儿）；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5147/5147678071a04497166ea5cf4c79c377.com/large/191c0002afd0a9ff55da"></p> 
<p>6、下手，稍用力抓拌均匀；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//377e/377e9b93b5621582b054544c73817a4f.com/large/19200002ad18ae71e6c7"></p> 
<p>7、加入玉米面和面粉；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0dd0/0dd08f3dafdbb574049cc1a0fa8e6acd.com/large/1921000281fabe1ef664"></p> 
<p>8、拌匀；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//cfed/cfed95b69da03e226f5ea636792051e2.com/large/191e0002ae7a7bf24d69"></p> 
<p>9、加入适量清水，少量多次，边加边拌匀；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7502/750295d5157c8e3d4786294d5cb7cf1b.com/large/1921000281f98742b264"></p> 
<p>10、拌成浓稠、稍有流动性的面糊；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//e593/e5931ea744150f38f79150abbdf8df57.com/large/191c0002afcfbc87dad8"></p> 
<p>11、烧热平底锅，加入适量食用油，将面糊舀入锅中，摊成小饼；</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5923/59231c4afdb04d45c1a940d762963ba0.com/large/191e0002ae7c1a910d59"></p> 
<p>12、中小火，煎至两面金黄，即可。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//48bd/48bdf93ace43b8311574c37f1eb9c0b2.com/large/191400049007f662d800"></p>胡萝卜 培根 癌症 胡椒粉这饼你不要错过，好吃不贵还抗癌保健康，味道比买的还要好！